# Testing Phases Index

> Modular, phase-based testing framework.
> Each phase builds on previous phases.

---

## Phase Dependencies

```
Phase 0: Setup
    ↓
Phase 1: Authentication
    ↓
Phase 2: Core Features
    ↓
Phase 3: Data Management
    ↓
Phase 4: User Features
    ↓
Phase 5: Advanced Features
    ↓
Phase 6: Integration Tests
```

---

## Phase Summary

| Phase | Name | Duration | Prerequisites |
|-------|------|----------|---------------|
| 0 | Setup & Environment | ~5 min | None |
| 1 | Authentication | ~10 min | Phase 0 |
| 2 | Core Features | ~15 min | Phase 1 |
| 3 | Data Management | ~15 min | Phase 2 |
| 4 | User Features | ~10 min | Phase 2 |
| 5 | Advanced Features | ~20 min | Phase 3-4 |
| 6 | Integration Tests | ~30 min | Phase 0-5 |

**Total Estimated Time**: ~105 minutes for full suite

---

## Creating New Phases

1. Copy `_PHASE_TEMPLATE.md`
2. Rename to `PHASE_XX_NAME.md`
3. Fill in test steps
4. Add to this index
5. Update dependencies

